  "title": "Marketing Manager / Marketing Associate (Fitness)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Summary</strong><br />We are looking for a marketing professional to drive <strong>viral social growth</strong> for a fitness brand/app. This role is highly hands-on and focuses on <strong>short-form content creation</strong>, trend-driven growth, and the use of <strong>AI tools</strong> to scale content production.</p><p>(Level and scope will be adjusted based on experience.)</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Plan and execute <strong>viral social media strategies</strong> on TikTok, Instagram Reels, and Shorts</p></li><li><p>Create, edit, and publish <strong>short-form fitness content</strong></p></li><li><p>Research trends, test content formats, and optimise based on performance</p></li><li><p>Use <strong>AI tools</strong> to generate scripts, visuals, voiceovers, and videos</p></li><li><p>Analyse content performance and continuously improve engagement and reach</p></li><li><p>Support marketing initiatives for a <strong>fitness app</strong>, including feature launches and campaigns</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Experience growing social media accounts organically</p></li><li><p>Strong skills in <strong>short-form video content creation</strong></p></li><li><p>Familiarity with <strong>AI tools for content generation</strong></p></li><li><p>Good understanding of social media trends and algorithms</p></li><li><p>Ability to move fast and iterate based on data</p></li></ul><h3>Nice to Have</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in the fitness or wellness industry</p></li><li><p>Experience marketing a consumer or mobile app</p></li><li><p>Influencer or creator collaboration experience</p></li></ul>",
